this is simply good etiquette. You can temporarily disable your sig in a single post by checking the box at the bottom in the section marked &quot;posting options.&quot;<br><br><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b>  Testing</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> - We have a forum specifically for testing and showing off artwork, html, sigs and pics. It's called &quot;The Comics&quot; - please use it, or use the &quot;preview&quot; feature, so we don't have to move your posts and the normal boards don't become cluttered with testing posts.<br><br>If we all follow these guidelines, everyone can enjoy MMDN without waiting an age for the pages to load, AND readers will be able to savor your sigs rather than be sick to death of seeing them 80 times in one thread. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub18.ezboard.com/ummdn.showPublicProfile?language=EN>MMDN</A> at: 8/2/01 7:35:11 am<br></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub18.ezboard.com/fmithanielmarrdailynewsfrm30.showMessage?topicID=12.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub18.ezboard.com/fmithanielmarrdailynewsfrm30.showMessage?topicID=8.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub18.ezboard.com/fmithanielmarrdailynewsfrm30.emailToFriend?topicID=9.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub18.ezboard.com/fmithanielmarrdailynewsfrm30.threadControl?topicID=9.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub18.ezboard.com/fmithanielmarrdailynewsfrm30.subscribeUn